data.description: Uncover the charm of Williston living - Your new three-bedroom Charmer awaits! As soon as you step through the front door, you will be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere that beckons you to call it your own. Imagine starting your mornings in the open-concept kitchen and dining area with real hardwood flooring, where natural light streams in through the windows, creating a picturesque breakfast nook, dining area and/or additional formal sitting area. Whip up your favorite meals in the well-appointed kitchen while chatting with family and friends seated at the dining table. As you explore the main level, you will discover two comfortable bedrooms and a full bathroom. But that's not all! The basement boasts an additional bedroom, a living room, full size modern bath, an office/gym space for all your creative and fitness needs, and a convenient laundry area. Step out into the fenced-in side yard, ideal for gardening, relaxing with friends and family, or letting your pets run free. With easy access to downtown Williston, you will enjoy the best of both worlds - the quiet charm of your backyard haven and the vibrant energy of city life just moments away. It's the perfect balance for those seeking the best of suburban living. Stand-out features include an attached side storage area, ceiling fans, updated appliances and abundance of natural light. Make your move this season, and spend Your Holidays in Your New Home!!
